text: Victor Kremer (31 July 1932 - 12 August 2010) was a Luxembourgian sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Luxembourg Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hesperange
